Class NameUIDCalculator

java.lang.Object
  lu.uni.geko.mapping.NameUIDCalculator
All Implemented Interfaces:
UIDCalculatorExt
public class NameUIDCalculator
extends Object
implements UIDCalculatorExt

An extension of the extension point lu.uni.geko.mapping.uidcalculatorext that implements the calculation of unique identifiers for mappings from pointcut to advice elements based on a name attribute.
